. The\nobtained results are consistent with the previous findings in the Anderson\nmodel and the exact solutions at the Toulouse point.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Feb 2018 01:52:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 May 2018 07:30:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 06:48:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-13"}
